title: Kyler Murray, NFL Mock Draft talk with Ryan Wilson (Football 1/15)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by CBS NFL Draft Expert Ryan Wilson to break down the latest news around the NFL, as well as Kyler Murray announcing his entry into the NFL Draft (19:30) and all the latest from Wilson's most recent mock draft (30:45) including whether the 49ers should draft Quinnen Williams (31:45), if the Giants should take Kyler Murray (35:30), other potential first-round quarterbacks (38:00), why Wilson likes Byron Murphy over Greedy Williams (43:00), what receiver the Steelers might target (45:30), Ed Oliver's status (49:00), Noah Fant's rise (51:15) and a small-school player who cracked Wilson's first round (55:00).
